l as possible for your customers.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","color_text":"#4d7c0f","color_background":"#f7fee7","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"#ffddbf","gradient_highlight":""}}},"block_order":["content-1","content-2","content-3","content-4"],"settings":{"heading":"Need help?","description":"<p>If you have any questions, you are always welcome to contact us. We'll get back to you as soon as possible, within 24 hours on weekdays.<\/p>"}},"video-hero":{"type":"video-hero","blocks":{"slide-1":{"type":"slide","settings":{"heading":"A Complete System for Professional Therapeutic Integration","heading_size":"title-md","heading_tag":"h2","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false}}},"block_order":["slide-1"],"name":"APPLICATION 1","settings":{"transparent_header":false,"video":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/bio-well_video-banner_formations-min.mp4","video_url":"","description":"","enable_video_autoplay":true,"enable_video_looping":true,"content_width":"medium","video_url_mobile":"","color_text":"#00c7ff","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_overlay":"#ffffff","overlay_opacity":60,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"divider":false,"full_width":true,"rounded":false}},"image_with_text_DMyFX4":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"image_nLFC9a":{"type":"image","settings":{"image_width":"custom","image_max_width":50,"image_max_width_mobile":50}},"heading_jgnt4k":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"What’s Included in the Full Therapist Pack","heading_size":"title-md","heading_tag":"h2","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false}},"text_dKEdg6":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>This pack combines equipment, training, and ongoing support into a single professional ecosystem.<\/p><ul><li><strong>Bio-Well 3.0 Camera<\/strong> (device + calibration unit + travel case + filters + 2-year warranty)<\/li><li><strong>Bio-Cor Device<\/strong> (frequency-based support with structured sound output)<\/li><li><strong>Level 1 Professional Training<\/strong> (videos + live practice)<\/li><li><strong>Personalized Onboarding<\/strong> (guided setup and first measurements)<\/li><li><strong>Unlimited Continuing Education<\/strong> (bi-weekly clinical Zoom meetings)<\/li><\/ul>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"text_line_height":1.6,"text_letter_spacing":0,"text_capitalize":false,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["image_nLFC9a","heading_jgnt4k","text_dKEdg6"],"name":"APPLICATION 2a","settings":{"image_height":"600px","image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","text_alignment":"left","content_position":"align-self-center","image_height_mobile":"400px","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_background_2":"#fafafa","gradient_background_2":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":72,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"image_with_text_37qzwz":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"image_DWaeyd":{"type":"image","settings":{"image_width":"custom","image_max_width":50,"image_max_width_mobile":50}},"heading_fD3KfU":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Information Transfer via Water<\/strong>","heading_size":"title-md","heading_tag":"h3","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false}},"text_aHcjGe":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Bio-Cor can also be used to imprint frequency information into water, which can then be consumed over time.<\/p><p>This approach allows the sound-based information to be integrated progressively, supporting continuity between sessions.<\/p><p>Water preparation offers a practical and non-invasive way to extend the therapeutic process into daily life, under the guidance of a practitioner.<\/p><p><\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"text_line_height":1.6,"text_letter_spacing":0,"text_capitalize":false,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["image_DWaeyd","heading_fD3KfU","text_aHcjGe"],"disabled":true,"name":"APPLICATION 2b","settings":{"image_height":"600px","image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","text_alignment":"left","content_position":"align-self-center","image_height_mobile":"400px","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_background_2":"#fafafa","gradient_background_2":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":72,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"rich_text_p7AnMT":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_Tt6EwY":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em><strong>Together, these elements form a coherent system designed for responsible professional use and long-term practice development.<\/strong><\/em><\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"text_line_height":1.6,"text_letter_spacing":0,"text_capitalize":false,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["text_Tt6EwY"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.name","settings":{"text_alignment":"center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","heading":"","heading_size":"title-md","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_width":"small","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false,"color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":100,"divider":false,"narrow":true,"rounded":false}},"timeline_Nym8Rq":{"type":"timeline","blocks":{"content_LxNqLR":{"type":"content","settings":{"subheading":"Measure","heading":"Capture objective indicators of stress, balance, and regulation.","heading_tag":"h3","text":"<p>Bio-Well captures electro-photonic data to assess stress load, functional balance, and autonomic nervous system regulation.<br\/>Measurements follow a standardized protocol to ensure reliability and reproducibility.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false}},"content_UP7FLk":{"type":"content","settings":{"subheading":"Analyze","heading":"Translate measurements into clear visual maps and structured reports.","heading_tag":"h3","text":"<p>Collected data is processed by the Bio-Well software and translated into visual maps, graphs, and structured indicators.<br\/>These outputs provide a clear overview of energetic patterns and areas of imbalance.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false}},"content_TxKaQa":{"type":"content","settings":{"subheading":"Interpret","heading":"Learn the methodology to read results correctly and avoid misinterpretation.","heading_tag":"h3","text":"<p>Through Level 1 professional training, practitioners learn how to read results accurately and place them in proper context.<br\/>The focus is on avoiding over-interpretation and maintaining a responsible, evidence-informed approach.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false}},"content_7RHKTm":{"type":"content","settings":{"subheading":"Support","heading":"Provide structured frequency-based post-session support under practitioner guidance.","heading_tag":"h3","text":"<p>Based on Bio-Well measurements, Bio-Cor can be used to support post-session integration through structured frequency-based output.<br\/>This step complements therapeutic work by encouraging regulation and continuity between sessions.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false}},"content_RgiFYT":{"type":"content","settings":{"subheading":"Follow Up","heading":"Track evolution over time and refine practice through ongoing clinical supervision.","heading_tag":"h3","text":"<p>Repeated measurements allow practitioners to observe evolution over time and document changes objectively.<br\/>Ongoing clinical Zoom sessions support continuous learning, case discussion, and refinement of professional practice.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false}}},"block_order":["content_LxNqLR","content_UP7FLk","content_TxKaQa","content_7RHKTm","content_RgiFYT"],"name":"How Bio-Cor Works","settings":{"show_navigation":true,"layout":"text_first","image_ratio":"square","image_ratio_mobile":"square","heading":"<strong>How Bio-Well + Bio-Cor Works<\/strong>","heading_size":"title-md","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"<p>A structured workflow from measurement to integration<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false,"color_text":"","color_background":"#f8f8f8","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":72,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false}},"rich_text_eiX83L":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_cCWkaP":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em><strong>The Starter Pack gives you a structured, measurable, and professional entry into Bio-Well practice.<\/strong><\/em><\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"text_line_height":1.6,"text_letter_spacing":0,"text_capitalize":false,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["text_cCWkaP"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.name","settings":{"text_alignment":"center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","heading":"","heading_size":"title-md","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_width":"small","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false,"color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":100,"divider":false,"narrow":true,"rounded":false}},"multicolumn_with_icons_HQEkge":{"type":"multicolumn-with-icons","blocks":{"column_NctAh9":{"type":"column","settings":{"icon":"support","custom_icon":"<svg fill=\"#000000\" width=\"800px\" height=\"800px\" viewbox=\"0 0 512 512\" enable-background=\"new 0 0 512 512\" id=\"Meditation\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xmlns:xlink=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/1999\/xlink\">\n\n<g>\n\n<g>\n\n<path d=\"M465.502,405.424c-1.061-9.484-5.17-18.139-11.703-24.881l26.646,17.551c1.822,1.201,3.885,1.803,5.951